line-height:.95;}\n  .z05-final p{max-width:720px;margin:18px auto 0;color:#d1c8bd;font-size:18px;line-height:1.55;}\n  @media(max-width:900px){.z05-hero,.z05-grid-2,.z05-photo-grid,.z05-copy-stack{grid-template-columns:1fr}.z05-hero{padding-top:56px;min-height:auto}.z05-hero-media{min-height:380px}.z05-stats,.z05-number-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.z05-build-card dl{grid-template-columns:1fr}.z05-build-card dt{border-bottom:0;padding-bottom:2px}.z05-build-card dd{padding-top:2px}}\n  @media(max-width:560px){.z05-wrap{width:min(100% - 24px,1180px)}.z05-hero h1{font-size:52px}.z05-stats,.z05-number-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}.z05-section{padding:52px 0}.z05-table th,.z05-table td{display:block;width:100%;padding:12px 14px}.z05-table th{padding-bottom:2px}.z05-table td{padding-top:2px}.z05-actions .z05-btn{width:100%;}}\n\u003c/style\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"z05-feature-shell\"\u003e\n  \u003csection class=\"z05-hero z05-wrap\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"z05-hero-copy\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"z05-eyebrow\"\u003eAAW Z Series Universal - AuAg Launch Edition\u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003ch1\u003e{{ product.title | default: \u0027Z05 AuAg Universal In-Ear Monitor\u0027 }}\u003c/h1\u003e\n      \u003cp class=\"z05-dek\"\u003eOne monitor, two musical personalities. Z05 AuAg pairs a tactile 10mm dynamic woofer with TwinCore switching, letting you choose between richer body or brighter focus without changing IEMs.\u003c/p\u003e\n      \u003cp class=\"z05-brand-slogan\"\u003eThose who listen will find the way.\u003cspan\u003e善听者，终能找到道路。\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n      \u003cul class=\"z05-meta\" aria-label=\"Z05 AuAg highlights\"\u003e\n        \u003cli\u003eTwinCore dual voice\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAuAg launch finish\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e10mm PET dynamic woofer\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e3.5 / 4.4 / Type-C ready\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003c/ul\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"z05-actions\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"z05-btn\" href=\"#z05-order\"\u003eConfigure Z05 AuAg\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca class=\"z05-btn secondary\" href=\"#z05-twincore\"\u003eHear the TwinCore story\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"z05-hero-media\"\u003e\n      \u003cimg src=\"{{ \u0027z05-auag-forged-carbon-faceplate-hero.jpg\u0027 | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg Launch Edition forged carbon faceplates with gold and silver foil lacing\"\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"z05-stat-strip\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-wrap z05-stats\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-stat\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eTwinCore\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBlue for weight and flow. Red for openness and focus. Two voicings built for real listening moods.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-stat\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eDynamic Bass\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA PET diaphragm 10mm woofer gives kick drums, bass guitars, and synth lines physical shape.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-stat\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHybrid Detail\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBalanced armatures bring vocal presence, separation, and upper harmonic air around the dynamic low end.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-stat\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eAuAg\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGold foil on the right shell, silver foil on the left, both set into forged carbon.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
