                     "z05_overview":  {
                                          "type":  "custom-liquid",
                                          "settings":  {
                                                           "section_visibility":  "always",
                                                           "custom_liquid":  "\u003cdiv class=\"z05-feature-shell\"\u003e\u003csection class=\"z05-section\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-wrap z05-grid-2\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp class=\"z05-kicker\"\u003eOverview\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eZ05 AuAg: one launch edition, two musical moods\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eZ05 AuAg is built for listeners who want a compact universal IEM that can move with their library. It can sound fuller and more enveloping, or cleaner and more incisive, while keeping the same hybrid-driver texture and AAW house sense of space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-number-cards\"\u003e\u003carticle class=\"z05-number-card\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"num\"\u003eAu\u003c/span\u003e\u003ch3\u003eGold Right Shell\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe right earpiece carries gold foil through the forged carbon faceplate and matching body shell, giving the pair its warm visual signature.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003carticle class=\"z05-number-card\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"num\"\u003eAg\u003c/span\u003e\u003ch3\u003eSilver Left Shell\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe left earpiece answers in silver foil, creating a deliberate precious-metal pairing rather than a random decorative accent.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003carticle class=\"z05-number-card\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"num\"\u003e02\u003c/span\u003e\u003ch3\u003eTwo Voices\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eTwinCore lets Z05 shift from easy musical weight to sharper audiophile focus with a physical switch on the shell.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ctable class=\"z05-table\"\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003eListening style\u003c/th\u003e\u003ctd\u003eSwitchable hybrid tuning for playlists, albums, portable sources, and long daily listening.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003eLow-end feel\u003c/th\u003e\u003ctd\u003eDynamic-driver punch with natural decay, useful for listeners who want bass texture instead of flat quantity.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003eTop-end feel\u003c/th\u003e\u003ctd\u003eBalanced armature speed and air for vocal lift, cymbal texture, and spatial definition.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003eFinish\u003c/th\u003e\u003ctd\u003eForged carbon faceplates and shells with side-specific gold and silver foil lacing.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
