                     "z05_engineering":  {
                                             "type":  "custom-liquid",
                                             "settings":  {
                                                              "section_visibility":  "always",
                                                              "custom_liquid":  "\u003cdiv id=\"z05-engineering\" class=\"z05-feature-shell\"\u003e\u003csection class=\"z05-section dark\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-wrap z05-grid-2\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp class=\"z05-kicker\"\u003eCraft \u0026 Sound\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003ePrecious-metal shell. Serious portable tuning.\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-build-card\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAAW Z05 AuAg\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cdl\u003e\u003cdt\u003eFormat\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eUniversal-fit hybrid in-ear monitor\u003c/dd\u003e\u003cdt\u003eLow End\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003e10mm PET diaphragm dynamic woofer\u003c/dd\u003e\u003cdt\u003eClarity\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eDedicated mid and super-high balanced armature drivers\u003c/dd\u003e\u003cdt\u003eVoice Control\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eTwinCore Crossover Switch System\u003c/dd\u003e\u003cdt\u003ePressure Flow\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eBass-Flow Vent Pressure System\u003c/dd\u003e\u003cdt\u003eFinish\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eForged carbon with gold foil right shell and silver foil left shell\u003c/dd\u003e\u003cdt\u003eIn The Box\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003e2-pin detachable cable, 3.5mm, 4.4mm balanced, Type-C terminations, carrying case, LiquidMorph eartips\u003c/dd\u003e\u003c/dl\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eZ05 AuAg is tuned for the listener who changes albums, sources, and moods through the day. The dynamic woofer gives drums and bass lines physical push, while the balanced armatures keep voices and upper harmonics clean enough for focused listening.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe AuAg finish gives the monitor its visual tension: gold on the right, silver on the left, both suspended in forged carbon and continued through the shell body. It looks collectible, but the purpose is still musical: fit, seal, texture, and control.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-photo-grid\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"{{ \u0027z05-auag-gold-silver-faceplate-pair.jpg\u0027 | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg gold and silver forged carbon faceplates\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"caption\"\u003eGold right shell and silver left shell, both built on forged carbon with full-shell foil lacing.\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"{{ \u0027z05-auag-twincore-switch-closeup.jpg\u0027 | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg TwinCore switch close-up\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"caption\"\u003eThe TwinCore switch gives Z05 AuAg its two listening profiles.\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
