                     "z05_faq":  {
                                     "type":  "custom-liquid",
                                     "settings":  {
                                                      "section_visibility":  "always",
                                                      "custom_liquid":  "\u003cdiv class=\"z05-feature-shell\"\u003e\u003csection class=\"z05-section\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-wrap z05-grid-2\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp class=\"z05-kicker\"\u003eFAQ\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eZ05 AuAg buying notes\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eShort answers for the questions listeners ask before choosing the AuAg Launch Edition.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-faq\"\u003e\u003cdetails open\u003e\u003csummary\u003eWhat does AuAg mean?\u003c/summary\u003e\u003cp\u003eAuAg names the Launch Edition decoration: Au for gold and Ag for silver. The right shell carries gold foil lacing, while the left shell carries silver foil lacing.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/details\u003e\u003cdetails\u003e\u003csummary\u003eIs this only a cosmetic edition?\u003c/summary\u003e\u003cp\u003eNo. The AuAg finish is the launch identity, but the listening story is the Z05 platform itself: dynamic bass, hybrid-driver clarity, Bass-Flow venting, and TwinCore switching.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/details\u003e\u003cdetails\u003e\u003csummary\u003eWhat does the TwinCore switch change?\u003c/summary\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt changes the overall voicing. Blue mode leans fuller, smoother, and more grounded. Red mode leans cleaner, more open, and more energetic. The effect is broader than a simple bass boost.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/details\u003e\u003cdetails\u003e\u003csummary\u003eWhat cable is included?\u003c/summary\u003e\u003cp\u003eZ05 AuAg includes a 2-pin detachable cable with swappable 3.5mm stereo, 4.4mm balanced, and Type-C terminations, plus LiquidMorph eartips for its universal-fit seal.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/details\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection class=\"z05-final\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eZ05 AuAg: choose the mood, keep the monitor\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThose who listen will find the way.\u003cbr\u003e善听者，终能找到道路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA forged-carbon launch edition with dynamic-driver body, balanced-armature detail, and TwinCore control for the way you actually listen.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-actions\" style=\"justify-content:center\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"z05-btn\" href=\"#z05-order\"\u003eBack to configuration\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
