                     "z05_accessories":  {
                                             "type":  "custom-liquid",
                                             "settings":  {
                                                              "custom_liquid":  "\u003cdiv class=\"z05-feature-shell\"\u003e\u003csection class=\"z05-section z05-accessory-section\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-wrap z05-grid-2\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp class=\"z05-kicker\"\u003eIncluded Accessories\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eOne cable for the sources you actually use\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe included 2-pin cable keeps Z05 AuAg ready for pocket DACs, balanced players, phones, laptops, and everyday listening without asking you to buy a second cable on day one.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ctable class=\"z05-table\"\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003eCable\u003c/th\u003e\u003ctd\u003e2-pin detachable cable with source-side swappable terminations.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003eTerminations\u003c/th\u003e\u003ctd\u003e3.5mm stereo, 4.4mm balanced, and Type-C connectors.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003eFit\u003c/th\u003e\u003ctd\u003eLiquidMorph eartips for comfort, seal, and repeatable bass response.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"z05-accessory-media\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"{{ \u0027z05-auag-liquidmorph-accessory-tray.jpg\u0027 | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg accessory tray with LiquidMorph eartips\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"caption\"\u003eAccessory tray context for the included LiquidMorph fit system and launch package.\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cstyle\u003e.z05-accessory-section{background:#f4f1ea;color:#111}.z05-accessory-section .z05-table{margin-top:24px}.z05-accessory-media{position:relative;min-height:480px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12);background:#111}.z05-accessory-media img{display:block;width:100%;height:100%;min-height:480px;object-fit:cover}.z05-accessory-media .caption{position:absolute;left:16px;right:16px;bottom:16px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.68);border:1px solid rgba(2